<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>bnḥzn wnkẖạf rbnạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- bnḥzn wnkẖạf rbmạ wạlsẖr yswd
 ạ̹nmạ
 ạ̉frạḥnạ bṭʿm ạlsmạ wtẖmạr ạlfrḥ htṭrḥ
 nfrḥ bạlḍạl ạlrạjʿ bdmwʿ ạltwbẗ wrạkʿ
 mrmy̱ fy ạlḥḍn ạlwạsʿ wạlsmạ bạltạyb nfrḥ
 ạlqrạr- whạnfrḥ brḍw hnfrḥ wnrnm lk wnsbḥ
 wmʿạk yạ ḥbybnạ hnfrḥ wnrm lk wnsbḥ
 wbrgẖm ạlgẖymẗ ạlswdạ dạ msyr ạlṣbḥ yṣbḥ
 2- lmạ ạlạ̉tʿạb twjʿnạ nṭlb wạ̹nt btsmʿnạ
 bạlrwḥ tyjy tjmʿnạ wqṣdk hytm wynjḥ
 bṣlạẗ wmʿạhạ ạ̉ṣwạmnạ wrjạʾ ḥy mṣbrnạ
 fy ạlbryẗ tsyrnạ wfy ạlbḥr ṭryq rạḥ tftḥ
 3- mʿ dmʿẗ btmlạ ʿynyạ ạ̉frạḥ ạlrwḥ tsbynạ
 lw ḥty̱ ạlkl ʿlynạ wklạb ạlsẖr btnbḥ
 wṣyạk btrfḥ sẖʿbk wạ̉hw jạy bkẖḍwʿ ysmʿ lk
 mhmạ bʿṣyạn kạn tạʿbk bṭạʿth btrtạḥ wbtfrḥ</lyrics>
<author>bhjt ʿdly, bhjt ʿdly</author>
<hymn_number>9842</hymn_number>
</song>